<h2>decktech.net</h2><b>location of article:</b> <hr>Wanted: Staff Writers and Admins for LotR! posted by DeckTech on Sat Dec 8 2001 <br><img src=/news/images/lotrlogo.gif align=right>DeckTech, rated #1 by Top Deck Magazine for online Star Wars strategy and info, is coming to Lord of the Rings and is currently scouring the Internet for a select few to write featured articles and administrate the site. <br>
<br>
Being on staff at DeckTech can really get your name out. How would you like to go to a local tournament hundreds of miles from where you live only to have the local players recognize you? It regularly happens with DeckTech writers! Not to mention he bonus tech points and insider info you will have access to! <br>
<br>
If you think you have what it takes to be a part of the DeckTech Team give us a shout at <a href="mailto:lotr@decktech.net"> lotr@decktech.net</a> and let us know what you would be interested in!<br>
<br>
For the players, By the players<br>
